---
By: Alphonsus Liguori
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 197
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - God's Will
---
Oh, the great folly of those who resist the will of God! They must of
necessity endure afflictions, because no one can prevent the accomplishment
of the Divine decrees. They must suffer without deriving any benefit from
their trials.
